This beautiful organza saree is from @cottagora 🧚🏼✨

Saree , Pastel Saree , Drape , Sage Color , Styling

If you don’t know me, I have a passion for styling clothes. It began with a capsule wardrobe, evolved into mixing and matching what I have, and now includes experimenting with different looks. I believe style can be anything—there are no limitations. It’s personal, it’s creative, and most importantly, it’s a reflection of YOU.

Most of what I’m wearing here is a collection of pieces I picked up from various travels. The top is from a boutique shop in Goa called @artjunacollection , the denim jeans are from a local store in Korea, and the necklace is from an exhibition in Gurugram.
